Although this recipe says to use spaghetti, you can enjoy these mouthwatering and flavourful turkey meatballs with any pasta dish of your choice, or in hotdog rolls to make delicious homemade turkey meatball subs.  If you are not a fan of turkey meat then you can substitute the turkey with chicken to create the same yummy sun-dried tomato and ricotta chicken meatballs.  ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Grilled chicken pitas with homemade potato wedges This recipe was found on halfbakedharvest.com